        "description": "<p>Querlo Chatbot plugin lets you install a free Querlo chat directly on your WordPress site pages. With one click, your website visitors can have a conversation with Querlo virtual assistant. A native Querlo chat button is easily recognizable by anyone and encourages trustful communication with all the features that a Querlo Customer Chat can offer.<\/p>\n<p>What makes Querlo Chatbot plugin stand out?<br \/>\n* Easy chat setup, no programming skills needed. Pre-built templates for several use cases are available.<br \/>\n* Direct communication with users on the page, without leaving the site.<br \/>\n* Instant receiving and replying to messages so your customers aren\u2019t lost.<br \/>\n* Chatbot can be used to automate responses to customer questions and reduce the amount of support agents.<\/p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/mGJeupFU1-g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLUwRtiIkQgVB8pFEA3ykNlF-FyOkkL56m\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"><\/iframe><\/span>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin to your FTP or other directory, then install it through the Plugins menu in your WordPress Dashboard.<\/li>\n<li>To use the Querlo Customer Chat, you need a Querlo account. Lifetime free plan available. Please create one at https:\/\/www.querlo.com\/register<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
